reviewText: This is a exceptional version of a much beloved opera. From the unique setting, to the astonishing voices, faultless acting and the superb production, it all speaks of a 'must have' for the committed opera lover. 10 out 10!

This is a very good production!! The stage is amazing!! and Rolando Villazn is singing better than ever!! it was on 2002 so Rolando at that time was coverin mor his sound! so the result was very good, in my personal opinion better than the recent time!!

Buy it!!!!!
